      <title>中国放松人民币兑美元汇率以测试7.3水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-17/china-moves-to-loosen-yuan-dollar-fixing-to-test-7-3-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一个月内第二次尝试放松对人民币的管制，为人民币兑美元测试7.30的心理水平打开了大门。彭博资讯首席亚洲外汇和利率策略师 Stephen Chiu 在彭博电视上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-17/china-moves-to-loosen-yuan-dollar-fixing-to-test-7-3-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:52:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国开始对金融监管机构和最大银行进行检查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/china-starts-inspections-of-financial-regulators-largest-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对其一些最大的国有银行、央行和主要监管机构启动了新的反腐败检查，这是自 2021 年一轮震惊整个行业的调查以来的首次广泛调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/china-starts-inspections-of-financial-regulators-largest-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利计划在中国进行多年来最大规模的裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/morgan-stanley-plans-biggest-round-of-china-job-cuts-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，摩根士丹利计划本周开始在亚太地区裁员约 50 个投行职位，其中至少 80% 的裁员将在香港和中国内地进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/morgan-stanley-plans-biggest-round-of-china-job-cuts-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平回绝德国总理肖尔茨遏制中国制造业的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-17/president-xi-rebuffs-pressure-from-chancellor-scholz-to-curb-chinese-manufacturing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平似乎反击了德国总统奥拉夫·肖尔茨(Olaf Scholz)遏制中国制造业的压力。习近平在北京对总理的讲话表明，中国可能不会动摇控制国内产业，因为他表示，负担得起的清洁技术出口激增有助于减轻通胀压力。珍妮·马什在彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-17/president-xi-rebuffs-pressure-from-chancellor-scholz-to-curb-chinese-manufacturing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:07:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国证监会寻求缓解退市担忧，中国小盘股上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/china-s-small-caps-gain-as-csrc-seeks-to-ease-delisting-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国最高证券监管机构试图缓解对财务状况不佳的公司可能退市的担忧，中国小盘股上涨，收复了本周早些时候抛售带来的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/china-s-small-caps-gain-as-csrc-seeks-to-ease-delisting-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:49:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南救援银行涉嫌 120 亿美元欺诈案：路透社</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/vietnam-starts-rescue-of-saigon-commercial-bank-reuters-lv34tq9k</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，越南已对一家与房地产大亨张美兰 (Truong My Lan) 有关的银行展开救援，张美兰上周因参与 120 亿美元的欺诈案而被判处死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/vietnam-starts-rescue-of-saigon-commercial-bank-reuters-lv34tq9k</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:26:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元止跌，股市暴跌暂时缓解：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市在暴跌后窄幅波动，导致主要基准指数几乎抹去今年的涨幅。随着交易员准备迎接美国长期较高的利率，货币再次成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大提高资本利得税，为住房筹集数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将提高企业和富人的资本利得税，以帮助支付数百亿美元的新支出，这些支出旨在使住房更加负担得起并改善年轻人的生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 F1 净零排放截止日期的临近，Formula E 为赛车行业展现了广阔的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/formula-e-shows-way-ahead-for-racing-as-f1-s-net-zero-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一级方程式是一个体育帝国，拥有摇滚明星车手、价值数十亿美元的车队和相当于一个非洲小国的碳足迹。电动方程式赛车是全电动方程式赛车，虽然规模只是电动方程式赛车的一小部分，但却是赛车运动的未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/formula-e-shows-way-ahead-for-racing-as-f1-s-net-zero-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛伊岛消防官员为拉海纳致命大火的反应辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hawaiian-electric-hits-40-year-low-ahead-of-maui-fire-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛伊岛消防局官员为他们对夏威夷历史上最致命的火灾的初步反应进行了辩护，称他们一直留在 8 月 8 日大火的现场，直到大火被完全扑灭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hawaiian-electric-hits-40-year-low-ahead-of-maui-fire-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
